This add-on adds many decorations, furniture, more villagers.

There is everything from kitchen utensils and bathroom equipment to things like a stove, shower products and entertainment-related things, like a pool table and a PC for games.

It is a great addon if you want more options to decorate your home.

Creator: twitter.com/ROBERTGAMER69

Add some useful decoration to your Minecraft worlds. A fridge, coffeemaker, toaster, microwave and more. The furniture actually works and its easy to use and with its new redesigned textures they will surely fit well in your house.Created by Lancelot, from Livecraft Team
